    "display_name": "Summarize a Current Event",
    "long_instructions": "## Summarize a Current Event\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to summarize a current news story or trending event.\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nCompare what happens if you ask for a summary in 2-3 sentences vs. a full paragraph.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nDoes the summary include the most important facts and stay neutral?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
